### Implementation Order

1. **myprofile.css** -- Add the desktop `.profile-editor-bg`, fix `.canvel-save-container` typo, add all new utility classes (`.is-saving`, `.gradient-selected`, focus-within rings, error toast, avatar hover opacity). This should be done first since the JSX changes depend on these classes existing.

2. **MyProfile.jsx** -- Fix all typos (`openRichTextEditor`, `handleClickCancelFontSelect`), remove duplicate setState, fix cancel-font-color logic, restructure all three save handlers for proper error handling, add `saveError` state and toast JSX, pass `gradientPicked` to `ProfileBackgroundPicker`.

3. **ProfileEditModal.jsx** -- Fix BarLoader color, add save button disabled/loading state, improve animation parameters, add backdrop click-to-close, avatar hover reveal.

4. **ProfileBackgroundPicker.jsx** -- Fix class name typo, fix button text casing, fix BarLoader color, add selected gradient visual indicator, add save disabled state.

5. **ProfileFontColorSelector.jsx** -- Fix prop name typo, fix BarLoader color, add hex value display, add save disabled state.

6. **ProfileHeroSection.jsx** -- Add title attributes to icon buttons.

